---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center pt-16 bg-slate-900 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Layered background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-950 via-slate-900 to-slate-800"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/80 via-transparent to-slate-900/40"></div>
    <!-- Blue glow -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[400px] bg-blue-600/8 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <!-- Grain overlay -->
    <div class="grain-overlay"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 text-center">
      <p class="text-blue-400/90 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-6 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        AI Automation &middot; Salt Lake City, Utah
      </p>

      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-[1.1] mb-6 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.35s;">
        I Make Your Business<br />
        <span class="text-blue-400">More Money</span> &mdash; or<br />
        <span class="text-blue-400">Save You Money</span> &mdash;<br class="sm:hidden" /> with AI.
      </h1>

      <div class="w-16 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-500 to-transparent mx-auto mb-6 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;"></div>

      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-300/90 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed font-light animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
        Most small businesses know AI could help. Almost none are using it. I fix that.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.65s;">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary text-white font-medium px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg text-sm tracking-wide">
          Book a Free Discovery Call
        </a>
        <a href="#services" class="btn-outline !border-slate-600 !bg-slate-800/50 text-slate-200 font-medium px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg text-sm tracking-wide hover:!bg-slate-700/50 hover:!border-slate-500">
          See What I Do
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Scroll indicator -->
      <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 1.2s;">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-slate-500">
          <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Scroll</span>
          <div class="w-px h-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-500 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem / Opportunity -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-offwhite">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center reveal">
        <p class="text-blue-600 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4">The Opportunity</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 leading-tight">
          Your Competitors Are About<br class="hidden sm:block" /> to Leave You Behind
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 mt-12">
        <div class="reveal bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold text-blue-600 font-serif mb-4">77%</div>
          <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg font-medium mb-2">of small businesses say AI would transform how they work.</p>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">They know the technology exists. They know it could save them hours every week. They just haven't figured out how to use it yet.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 font-serif mb-4">5%</div>
          <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg font-medium mb-2">are actually using AI right now.</p>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">That means 95% of small businesses are doing things the slow, expensive way. If you move now, you'll be ahead of almost everyone in your market.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12 reveal">
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          That gap is your opportunity. I help you close it &mdash; with real AI tools built for your specific business, not some one-size-fits-all product you'll never use.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section divider -->
  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section id="services" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 sm:mb-20 reveal">
        <p class="text-blue-600 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4">What I Build</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-5">AI That Works While You Sleep</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed">Simple, practical AI tools that save you time and money. No complicated software. No steep learning curve. It just works.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8 stagger-children">
        <!-- AI Customer Service -->
        <div class="reveal card-hover bg-offwhite rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-slate-100">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 mb-6">
            <!-- Chat bubble icon -->
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.625 12a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H8.25m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H12m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0h-.375M21 12c0 4.556-4.03 8.25-9 8.25a9.764 9.764 0 01-2.555-.337A5.972 5.972 0 015.41 20.97a5.969 5.969 0 01-.474-.065 4.48 4.48 0 00.978-2.025c.09-.457-.133-.901-.467-1.226C3.93 16.178 3 14.189 3 12c0-4.556 4.03-8.25 9-8.25s9 3.694 9 8.25z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">AI Customer Service</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            A chatbot on your website that answers customer questions and captures leads &mdash; 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. It works while you sleep.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Answers common questions instantly
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Captures leads and sends them to your inbox
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Knows your business inside and out
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Voice Receptionist -->
        <div class="reveal card-hover bg-offwhite rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-slate-100">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 mb-6">
            <!-- Phone icon -->
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">AI Voice Receptionist</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            A 24/7 AI receptionist that answers your phone, books appointments, and takes messages &mdash; so you never miss a call.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Never miss a call &mdash; answers 24/7
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Books appointments and captures caller info
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Routes urgent calls to your cell
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Email & Admin Automation -->
        <div class="reveal card-hover bg-offwhite rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-slate-100">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 mb-6">
            <!-- Envelope icon -->
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Email & Admin Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Stop spending hours on email. AI handles sorting, drafting responses, and following up &mdash; so you can focus on the work that actually makes you money.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Sorts and prioritizes your inbox automatically
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Drafts replies you can send with one click
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Follows up with leads so nobody falls through the cracks
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Content Generation -->
        <div class="reveal card-hover bg-offwhite rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-slate-100">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 mb-6">
            <!-- Document icon -->
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Content That Writes Itself</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Social media posts, product descriptions, newsletters &mdash; created in minutes instead of hours. Sounds like you, reads like a pro.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Social media posts in your brand voice
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Product descriptions that sell
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Weekly newsletters ready to send
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Data & Reporting -->
        <div class="reveal card-hover bg-offwhite rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-slate-100">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 mb-6">
            <!-- Chart icon -->
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Data & Reporting</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Turn messy spreadsheets into clear reports. Automate invoices, inventory tracking, and scheduling &mdash; no more manual data entry.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Automatic reports from your existing data
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Invoice and scheduling automation
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Dashboards you can actually understand
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 bg-slate-900 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-900 to-slate-800"></div>
    <div class="grain-overlay"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 sm:mb-20 reveal">
        <p class="text-blue-400/90 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4">Simple Process</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-5">Three Steps. That's It.</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed">No long contracts. No confusing process. Here's exactly how it works.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="reveal text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="font-serif text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold step-number mb-4">01</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Free Discovery Call</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            You tell me what's eating your time. I listen. We figure out where AI can make the biggest difference for your business. No cost, no commitment.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="reveal text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="font-serif text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold step-number mb-4">02</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">I Build Your Solution</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            I create a custom AI tool designed for exactly what your business needs. Most projects are delivered in 1&ndash;2 weeks. You see progress the whole way.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="reveal text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="font-serif text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold step-number mb-4">03</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">You Save Time & Money</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Your AI starts working immediately. I maintain it monthly so it keeps running smoothly. You focus on growing your business &mdash; not fighting with technology.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-16 reveal">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary text-white font-medium px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg text-sm tracking-wide inline-block">
          Book Your Free Call
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section id="pricing" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-offwhite">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 sm:mb-20 reveal">
        <p class="text-blue-600 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4">Investment</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-5">Honest Pricing</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed">Every business is different. Here's a straight answer on what things cost.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 sm:gap-6 mb-10">
          <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium mb-2">Custom Solutions</p>
            <p class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">$500 &ndash; $5,000</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2">Depends on what you need. Simple automations cost less. Bigger systems cost more. I'll give you an exact number before we start.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium mb-2">Monthly Maintenance</p>
            <p class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Affordable</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2">A fraction of the setup cost. I keep your AI tools running, updated, and working right. You never have to touch them.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium mb-2">Discovery Call</p>
            <p class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600">Free</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2">No commitment. No pressure. We talk about your business, I tell you what AI can do for you. If it's not a fit, we part as friends.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm text-center sm:text-left">
              <span class="font-medium text-slate-800">Most clients see a return in the first month.</span><br />
              The time you save is worth more than what you pay.
            </p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary text-white font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm tracking-wide shrink-0">
              Get a Free Quote
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section divider -->
  <div class="section-divider"></div>

